---
const title = "Caaligo | Blog";
---
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/caaligo_icon.png">
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
  <title>{title}</title>
</head>

<body>

  <aside class="sidebar">

    <div class="brand">
      <img src="/channellogo.jpg" alt="Caaligo Logo" class="channel-logo" />
      <h1>CAALIGO</h1>
      <p>
        Minecraft creator making videos,
        mods, and more.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="search">
      <input type="text" placeholder="Search..." />
    </div>

    <nav>
      <h3>Navigation</h3>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/content">Videos</a>
      <a href="/moe">Obsidian Edition</a>
      <a href="/blog" class="active">Blog</a>
      <a href="/community">Community</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
    </nav>

<nav>
  <h3>Socials</h3>
  <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Caaligo/featured" target="_blank">YouTube</a>
  <a href="https://discord.gg/Hcg6yWWSjn" target="_blank">Discord</a>
  <a href="https://www.curseforge.com/members/caaligo/projects" target="_blank">CurseForge</a>
  <a href="https://www.instagram.com/caaligo_?igsh=cHJyMm4wMjV2eThq" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
  <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@caaligo?_r=1&_t=ZT-980bISurc8j" target="_blank">TikTok</a>
  <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@LeoCaaligula" target="_blank">Caaligula</a>
</nav>

  </aside>

  <main class="main">

    <article class="paper">

      <div class="hero">
        <p class="label">CAALIGO'S BLOG</p>
        <h2>Blog</h2>
        <p>Thoughts, updates, and deep dives.</p>
      </div>

      <hr />

      <section class="blog-post">
        <small class="post-date">July 14, 2026</small>
        <h2>New Post</h2>
        <div class="post-content">
        <h3>Caedes Video II</h3>
          <p>I just had one of the biggest brain-blasts in history and it all has to do specifically with the way I was raised as a kid.</p>
          <p>I'm obviously not going to spoil what it is, but all of the religious information that I have retained within me for so long because of my upbringing and the school that I went to just helped me out so much. </p>
          <p>I'm obviously talking about Caedes, as I've been working on the script for the next video since yesterday. I anticipate the video being done probably by this Friday, as it's not too terribly hard to make those forms of videos. A lot of it comes down to just rewatching all of the content from the channel, explaining what happens in each episode, and then cross referencing theories and stuff. </p>
          <p>Funnily enough a lot of the theories come to me as I watch the videos, so that's cool. And of course as I rewatch them.</p>
          <p>Additionally I do plan on updating MOE here soon, I just want to get this video done and then I'll most likely start working on that again. Someone made me think to do a Slip (Nether) update, so that's what it'll most likely be.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="blog-post">
        <small class="post-date">July 13, 2026</small>
        <div class="post-content">
        <h3>Website Opening</h3>
          <p>Here's the start to my website. Not much to say here other than I'll be using this domain to do a bunch of stuff, including the server that I'll be getting up and running here in a week or so.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

    </article>

  </main>

</body>
</html>

<style>
:root {
  --accent: #58c7ff;
  --paper: #ffffff;
}

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-image: url("/space.jpg");
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  background-attachment: fixed;
}

/* Sidebar Styling (Matches your other pages) */
.sidebar {
  position: fixed;
  width: 280px;
  height: 100vh;
  background: rgba(17,20,38,0.95);
  padding: 35px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  color: white;
  overflow-y: auto;
}

.channel-logo {
  width: 110px;
  height: 110px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  object-fit: cover;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  border: 2px solid var(--accent);
  box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(88, 199, 255, 0.2);
}

.brand h1 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 42px;
  letter-spacing: 5px;
}

.brand p {
  color: #b8bfd8;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.search input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 10px;
  margin: 25px 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  background: #20243b;
  border: 1px solid #333;
  color: white;
}

nav h3 {
  color: var(--accent);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-size: 13px;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
}

nav a {
  display: block;
  color: #cfd5ed;
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 8px 0;
}

nav a:hover, nav a.active {
  color: white;
}

nav a.active {
  font-weight: bold;
  border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
  padding-left: 10px;
  margin-left: -12px;
}

/* Main Content Area */
.main {
  margin-left: 280px;
  padding: 50px;
  min-height: 100vh;
}

.paper {
  max-width: 850px;
  margin: auto;
  background: var(--paper);
  padding: 55px;
  box-shadow: 0 20px 60px black;
}

.hero {
  text-align: center;
}

.label {
  color: #777;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
}

hr {
  border: none;
  border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
  margin: 40px 0;
}

/* Blog Post Specifics */
.blog-post {
  margin-bottom: 60px;
}

.post-date {
  color: #777;
  font-family: monospace;
}

.post-content {
  margin-top: 20px;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: #333;
}

@media(max-width:900px) {
  .sidebar {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }
  .main {
    margin-left: 0;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .paper {
    padding: 30px;
  }
}
</style>